Params: {3: 'City 075, Core Area of the underground cavern.'}
{3: 'The holo-map in front clearly shows red dots moving around the city. Based on their distance, it is obvious that they are closing in.'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Miss Luna, it is the Gray Ravens with their human commandant.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Are you not going to take action?', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "If they've found this place, that means...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "She's not on a mission. She must be slacking on the job.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: 'Since our guests have arrived at the door, there is no reason not to entertain them.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Alpha and Roland proceed in opposite directions. Luna looks at the holo-map and extends her hand out at the approaching red dots.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: 'Maybe you will understand once you remember.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Luna', 3: '...How despicable and selfish humans truly are.', 4: '1'}
